StartReconciliationLate is an ActionForm
    action is Open.StartReconciliationLate
    title is "StartReconciliation"
    Layout
        header3 of "EnterAReasonForStartingTask_<CloseTask.TaskName>LateForTheReconciliation:<DerivedReconciliationAccountDescription>"
        visible when (ReconciliationManagementGroup.CloseManagementGroup.StartLateReasonCodeRequired)
            paragraph
                reason code
                reason code.Description
                    no label
                    display as text
        paragraph
            text of "<CloseTaskStartingLateMessage>"
                italics
        single column
            PrmComment
                label is "Comment"
                use text area of 10 lines
